    4792/ FDAA:                ;**********
    4793/ FDAA:                ;*   register [<name>]  - prints the user regs
    4794/ FDAA:                ;*and opens them for modification.  <name> is
    4795/ FDAA:                ;*the first register opened (default = P).
    4796/ FDAA:                ;*   Subcommands:
    4797/ FDAA:                ;* [<nn>]<space>  Opens the next register.
    4798/ FDAA:                ;* [<nn>]<cr>     Return.
    4799/ FDAA:                ;*    The register value is only changed if
    4800/ FDAA:                ;*    <nn> is entered before the subcommand.
    4801/ FDAA:                ;**********
    4802/ FDAA:                ;*x[] = reglist
    4803/ FDAA:                ;*a = wskip(); a = upcase(a);
    4804/ FDAA:                ;*if(a != cr)
