    4853/ FDF0: 39                             RTS
    4854/ FDF1: 36             REG6            PSHA
    4855/ FDF2: 3C                             PSHX
    4856/ FDF3: 7D 00 A8                       TST   COUNT
    4857/ FDF6: 27 14                          BEQ   REG8            ;jump if no input
